html(ng-app='myApp')
	head
		title mkShortcuts Example
		
		link(href='//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
		script(src='//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.2.2/angular.min.js')

		script(src='js/app.js')
		script(src='dist/mk-shortcuts.min.js')
	
	body(my-kb-manager='kb')
		.container
			.row
				h2.text-center Shortcuts Example
				
				.col-md-2.col-md-offset-4
					| Keyboard events on this page are handled by the Keyboard Manager. 
					| Try doing Ctr+A or Ctrl+Z to see the effect.

				.col-md-2
					table.table
						tr(ng-repeat='log in logs track by $index') 
							td {{($index+1) + ' ' + log}}				